{"tid":2092214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劍橋擬褫奪林鄭院士銜","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:41:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"743fe80042d6d203127e764539e998f7ff3f3e7b","tid":2092214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/7254TVTR3EPPBGMPWNTQUHE2LI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2F7254TVTR3EPPBGMPWNTQUHE2LI%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=205e62cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2F7254TVTR3EPPBGMPWNTQUHE2LI%2F&h=1c28bcea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/7254TVTR3EPPBGMPWNTQUHE2LI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n劍橋擬褫奪林鄭院士銜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國劍橋大學沃爾森學院（Wolfson College, Cambridge）正考慮褫奪香港行政長官林鄭月娥的榮譽院士名銜。沃爾森學院院長克拉克教授（Professor Jane Clarke）發表聲明稱，沃爾森學院強烈支持保障學院所有成員的人權和言論自由，因此對香港近日實施港版國安法後發生的事件深感關注，校董會正檢討林鄭月娥作為學院榮譽院士的身份。林鄭月娥2017年獲沃爾森學院頒授榮譽院士名銜，學院網站當時稱，37位榮譽院士名銜是頒發給享有崇高聲譽的傑出人士。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒隨時中招 譚耀宗：明眼人識分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hexymCBzzJGjXbjEMFtKzOdTa0U=/680x321/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JOGGKOEMFQUV5T6GHZFHCUILFA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhexymCBzzJGjXbjEMFtKzOdTa0U%3D%2F680x321%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJOGGKOEMFQUV5T6GHZFHCUILFA.gif&h=316060b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭或被劍橋大學沃爾森學院褫奪榮譽院士名銜。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三英議員斥無能好鬥<br />\n<br />\n去年林鄭月娥因硬推《逃犯條例》<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n褫奪她的榮譽院士名銜。<br />\n<br />\n三名英國上議院議員去年11月去信劍橋大學校長、<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n引發200萬人走上街頭示威。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學網頁/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"f656d753b26f9424521cac165c4a50eadbc4d204","tid":2092214,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"正檢視"},{"pid":"14cca3c6c41cfd3af64fdc07bb705112eb13ab34","tid":2092214,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"38條。。。<br />\n<br />\n又拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a865b449fce5e01be142920ebd0a4359090285a","tid":2092214,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"Luke有無幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26b354014d2fc63f08e11b219b599471ffb8142","tid":2092214,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc6d858e6c46b28a9393e68087558140b4a1268","tid":2092214,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrxqPFJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrxqPFJ.gif&h=a2d3b580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c9b04566f21077b1c4ece4d06d736b738b66245","tid":2092214,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"俾舊事頭婆摵柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9748e942a9abddf5dd76f84d16bb324fe498c7f3","tid":2092214,"uid":39200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:18:08.000Z","msg":"褫奪佢無用, 都慣左做垃圾<br />\n褫奪佢老公同個仔, 包佢即刻變節"},{"pid":"5433079362e2363539ab0abe4dcd338950e4c69d","tid":2092214,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr